{"title":"后患无穷","authors":["池北偶朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":4,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"后患无穷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗朱根华画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星球大战计划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年胎死腹中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今改头换面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出来一个变种。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标榜防御导弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无异盘马弯弓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦盾牌具备，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放箭有恃无恐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷战年代搁置，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缓和时期启用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破坏国际协议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不顾和平呼声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非想搞威慑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或要刺激军工？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此种危险动作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必将后患无穷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打破力量平衡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军备竞赛解冻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倘若一意孤行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能遭到围攻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑袋应当清醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫逆潮流而动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不改弦易辙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"须知此路不通！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}